<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fuelsgate | Truck Status Update Request</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .margin {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .marginY {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        td {
            padding: auto 15px;
        }

        .salutation p {
            margin-top: 10px !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table style="width: 100%; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 20px 0;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center;">
                <table
                    style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; background-color: #1f2937; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
                            <img src="https://fuelsgate.com/assets/images/logo-white.png" alt="Fuelsgate Logo"
                                style="max-width: 150px; height: auto;">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px;">
                            <h1
                                style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">
                                Truck Status Update Request
                            </h1>

                            <div class="salutation">
                                <p class="margin" style="color: #374151;">Dear Admin,</p>
                            </div>

                            <p class="margin" style="color: #374151;">
                                A truck owner has requested to update their truck status to "available" and requires
                                admin approval.
                            </p>

                            <table
                                style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 6px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td
                                        style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">
                                        Truck Owner:</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280;">
                                        <%= TruckOwner %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td
                                        style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">
                                        Owner Email:</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280;">
                                        <%= OwnerEmail %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td
                                        style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">
                                        Truck Number:</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280;">
                                        <%= TruckNumber %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td
                                        style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">
                                        Truck Capacity:</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280;">
                                        <%= TruckCapacity %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td
                                        style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">
                                        Depot:</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280;">
                                        <%= Depot %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td
                                        style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">
                                        Current Status:</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280;">
                                        <%= CurrentStatus %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">Requested Status:</td>
                                    <td style="padding: 15px; color: #10b981; font-weight: 600;">
                                        <%= RequestedStatus %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <p class="margin" style="color: #374151;">
                                Please review this request and take appropriate action through the admin dashboard.
                            </p>

                            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                                <a href="<%= AdminDashboardUrl %>"
                                    style="background-color: #1f2937; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block;">
                                    Review in Admin Dashboard
                                </a>
                            </div>

                            <p class="margin" style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
                                <strong>Request Time:</strong>
                                <%= RequestTime %>
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="padding: 20px 40px; background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; text-align: center;">
                            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                                This is an automated notification from Fuelsgate Admin System
                            </p>
                            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; margin: 5px 0 0 0;">
                                Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Fuelsgate. All rights reserved.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>